            Share your workstation setup and vote on others. 
            See how your setup ranks against the community!
          </p>
          
          <div className="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <Link
              href="/signup"
              className="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
            >
              Get Started
            </Link>
            <Link
              href="/login"
              className="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 transition"
            >
              Sign In
            </Link>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
            <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div className="text-3xl mb-3">ğŸ“¸</div>
              <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Upload Your Setup</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-600">Share 3-5 photos of your workstation</p>
            </div>
            <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div className="text-3xl mb-3">âš”ï¸</div>
              <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Vote & Compare</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-600">Choose between two setups side-by-side</p>
